Well, since this being the first time ever using Hammer, a Fy map has been born =]. I present to you "Fy_DeadLocked".

-----

...After being tricked by an anonymous tipper, the Counter Terrorists find themselves in a dire situation. The Terrorists have locked the gate and seem to have unleashed an ambush upon the Cts.....

-----

Just aliitle backstory lol. This is a simple 5v5 FY map in a warhouse esque setting. There are 4 house surrounding a bomb site in the middle. 
It proves to be a great enjoyment to all. Enjoi!

If anything my email is Dinokind@gmail.com
